20
00:02:24,294 --> 00:02:26,087
<font color="#FFFFFF">Give us a kiss. Come on. Up, up.</font>

21
00:02:26,254 --> 00:02:28,549
<font color="#FFFFFF">Take Marge's suitcase upstairs.</font>

22
