<font color="#FFFFFF">Just a bit more. That's a boy.</font>

29
00:02:56,367 --> 00:02:58,370
<font color="#FFFFFF">You wanna try
a little drop of brandy?</font>

30
00:02:58,537 --> 00:03:02,582
<font color="#FFFFFF">A little drop of brandy-brandy
windy-wandy for Rippy-pippy-pooh?</font>

31
00:03:04,084 --> 00:03:05,877
<font color="#FFFFFF">What are you smirking at?</font>

32
00:03:06,044 --> 00:03:07,879
<font color="#FFFFFF">Where did you send the boy,
Vernon?</font>

33
00:03:08,087 --> 00:03:11,383
<font color="#FFFFFF">St. Brutus'. It's a fine
institution for hopeless cases.</font>

34
00:03:11,550 --> 00:03:14,552
<font color="#FFFFFF">Do they use a cane
