35
00:03:18,014 --> 00:03:19,348
<font color="#FFFFFF">Oh, yeah.</font>

36
00:03:19,557 --> 00:03:22,227
<font color="#FFFFFF">Yeah. I've been beaten loads of times.</font>

37
00:03:22,394 --> 00:03:24,979
<font color="#FFFFFF">Excellent. I won't have this
namby-pamby...</font>

38
00:03:25,187 --> 00:03:28,317
<font color="#FFFFFF">wishy-washy nonsense about
not beating people who deserve it.</font>

39
00:03:28,483 --> 00:03:31,611
<font color="#FFFFFF">You mustn't blame yourself
about how this one turned out.</font>

40
00:03:31,777 --> 00:03:35,699
<font color="#FFFFFF">It's all to do with blood.
Bad blood will out.</font>

41
00:03:35,865 --> 00:03:38,034
<font color="#FFFFFF">What is it the boy's father did,
Petunia?</font>

42
00:03:38,201 --> 00:03:41,204
<font color="#FFFFFF">Nothing. He didn't work.
He was unemployed.</font>

43
00:03:41,371 --> 00:03:44,207
<font color="#FFFFFF">- And a drunk too, no doubt?
- That's a lie.</font>

44
00:03:44,373 --> 00:03:46,918
<font color="#FFFFFF">- What did you say?
- My dad wasn't a drunk.</font>

45
00:03:49,921 --> 00:03:54,009
<font color="#FFFFFF">Don't worry. Don't fuss, Petunia.
I have a very firm grip.</font>

46
00:03:54,175 --> 00:03:56,010
<font color="#FFFFFF">I think it's time you went to bed.</font>

47
00:03:56,177 --> 00:03:59,430
<font color="#FFFFFF">Quiet, Vernon. You, clean it up.</font>

48
00:04:00,806 --> 00:04:03,810
<font color="#FFFFFF">Actually, it's nothing to do
