51
00:04:12,193 --> 00:04:13,861
<font color="#FFFFFF">Shut up! Shut up!</font>

52
00:04:18,867 --> 00:04:20,619
<font color="#FFFFFF">Right.</font>

53
00:04:20,786 --> 00:04:22,913
<font color="#FFFFFF">Let me tell you...</font>

54
00:04:44,350 --> 00:04:46,478
<font color="#FFFFFF">Vernon!</font>

55
00:04:49,523 --> 00:04:51,316
<font color="#FFFFFF">Vernon! Vernon, do something!</font>

56
00:05:34,776 --> 00:05:36,778
<font color="#FFFFFF">Stop!</font>

57
00:05:39,363 --> 00:05:41,908
<font color="#FFFFFF">I've got you, Marge. I've got you.</font>

58
00:05:45,370 --> 00:05:47,331
<font color="#FFFFFF">- Hold on, hold on.
- Get off.</font>

59
00:05:48,624 --> 00:05:50,417
<font color="#FFFFFF">- Don't you dare!
- Sorry.</font>

60
00:05:51,627 --> 00:05:53,461
<font color="#FFFFFF">Oh, Vernon.</font>

61
00:05:53,629 --> 00:05:55,379
<font color="#FFFFFF">Oh, God.</font>

62
00:05:55,547 --> 00:05:57,341
<font color="#FFFFFF">Marge!</font>

63
00:06:04,389 --> 00:06:06,600
<font color="#FFFFFF">Please!</font>

64
00:06:07,225 --> 00:06:09,435
<font color="#FFFFFF">Marge!</font>

65
00:06:10,519 --> 00:06:13,689
<font color="#FFFFFF">Come back!</font>

66
00:06:37,673 --> 00:06:40,091
<font color="#FFFFFF">You bring her back!
