110
00:11:26,669 --> 00:11:29,298
<font color="#FFFFFF">He was a big supporter of...</font>

111
00:11:29,798 --> 00:11:31,299
<font color="#FFFFFF">You-Know-Who.</font>

112
00:11:32,009 --> 00:11:33,885
<font color="#FFFFFF">I reckon you've heard of him.</font>

113
00:11:34,052 --> 00:11:35,636
<font color="#FFFFFF">Yeah.</font>

114
00:11:35,803 --> 00:11:37,139
<font color="#FFFFFF">Him I've heard of.</font>

115
00:11:39,807 --> 00:11:42,476
<font color="#FFFFFF">Ernie, two double-deckers
