155
00:14:48,746 --> 00:14:51,207
<font color="#FFFFFF">wander.</font>

156
00:14:52,793 --> 00:14:55,671
<font color="#FFFFFF">Right! You gonna move
that bus or what?</font>

157
00:16:14,457 --> 00:16:16,500
<font color="#FFFFFF">Housekeeping.</font>

