- Mrs. Weasley.</font>

176
00:17:15,519 --> 00:17:17,688
<font color="#FFFFFF">- Good to see you, dear.
- Good to see you.</font>

177
00:17:17,855 --> 00:17:19,189
<font color="#FFFFFF">- Got everything?
- Yes.</font>

178
00:17:19,355 --> 00:17:21,525
<font color="#FFFFFF">- Yes? All your books?
- It's all upstairs.</font>

179
00:17:21,692 --> 00:17:23,109
<font color="#FFFFFF">- Your clothes?
- Everything.</font>

180
00:17:23,277 --> 00:17:24,694
<font color="#FFFFFF">- Good boy.
- Thank you.</font>

181
00:17:24,862 --> 00:17:26,738
<font color="#FFFFFF">- Harry Potter.
