182
00:17:26,904 --> 00:17:30,409
<font color="#FFFFFF">- Harry, wonder if I might have a word?
- Yeah, sure.</font>

183
00:17:30,616 --> 00:17:33,244
<font color="#FFFFFF">- Hermione.
- Good morning, Mr. Weasley.</font>

184
00:17:33,412 --> 00:17:37,039
<font color="#FFFFFF">- Looking forward to a new term?
- Yeah. It should be great.</font>

185
00:17:40,126 --> 00:17:43,963
<font color="#FFFFFF">Harry, some within the Ministry
